Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子，抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子，抓到了
